{"tid":2028705,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港股瀉逾800點 地產股重創 滙控創逾11年低","createTime":"2020-05-22T02:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T04:10:36.000Z","uid":253978,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0dffaa58f02797c5bf2e63259c5712944df11be0","tid":2028705,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"隔晚美股道指收市挫101點，加上市場關注人大為香港進行國家安全立法，港股今早大跌逾八百點，藍籌股全線下跌。<br />\n<br />\n恒指低開523點或2.15%，報23756，跌幅隨即擴大，截至10時15分，恒指大跌827點，報23452，創4月6日以來即一個半月低位，盡失主要平均線，包括最下方的50天線(約23814)。<br />\n<br />\n國企指數跌268點，報9581。<br />\n<br />\n內地股市向下，跌幅較細，上證指數現報2845，跌22點或0.8%。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊(00700)挫2.8%，報421.2元；阿里(09988)挫3%。<br />\n<br />\n金融股受壓，友邦(01299)挫4.7%；滙控(00005)挫3%，低見37.25元，創超過11年新低。<br />\n<br />\n憂慮社會形勢，地產股重創，新地(00016)插7.2%；信置(00083)插7%；恒地(00012)挫5.6%；新世界(00017)跌近7%。收租股方面，太古地產(01972)插7.3%；九倉置業(01997)瀉8%，暫為最大跌幅藍籌；領展(00823)亦瀉7.3%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/stockConnect/article/2472464/港股瀉逾800點+地產股重創+滙控創逾11年低\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2FstockConnect%2Farticle%2F2472464%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E7%80%89%E9%80%BE800%E9%BB%9E%2B%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E8%82%A1%E9%87%8D%E5%89%B5%2B%E6%BB%99%E6%8E%A7%E5%89%B5%E9%80%BE11%E5%B9%B4%E4%BD%8E&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzYyfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=0bb9b620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/stockConnect/article/2472464/港股瀉逾800點+地產股重創+滙控創逾11年低</a>"},{"pid":"8a12ee03ac9ff3ccf0f55d74e7c6998d7c0ff66c","tid":2028705,"uid":61030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:55:19.000Z","msg":"你搵8毛賺到笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41193abb0dd85e9a0486dd83a137abbb8260fec","tid":2028705,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a12ee03ac9ff3ccf0f55d74e7c6998d7c0ff66c","tid":2028705,"uid":61030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:55:19.000Z","msg":"你搵8毛賺到